OL,3,CPopular shop announces closure due to
OL,4,C'unbearable trading conditions'
OL,6,FA popular farm shop on the outskirts
OL,7,Fof Cardiff has announced it will be
OL,8,Fshutting its doors due to "unbearable
OL,9,Ftrading conditions".
OL,11,FCefn Mably Farm Park's shop, the Moody
OL,12,FSow, said it will be closing down on
OL,13,FSunday 25 January because of rising
OL,14,Ftaxes.
