OL,3,CPopular shop announces closure due to
OL,4,C'unbearable trading conditions'
OL,6,FIt blamed a combination of rising
OL,7,Femployer's National Insurance
OL,8,FContributions, brought in by the UK
OL,9,FGovernment in April last year, rising
OL,10,Fbusiness rates - controlled here by
OL,11,Fthe Welsh Government, and rising
OL,12,Finflation.
OL,14,FCefn Mably Park Farm owner, Rhys
OL,15,FEdwards, posted a video on social
OL,16,Fmedia on Thursday (15 January)
OL,17,Fevening, explaining the difficult
OL,18,Fchoice.
