OL,3,CPopular shop announces closure due to
OL,4,C'unbearable trading conditions'
OL,6,FHe said: "The trading and business
OL,7,Fconditions in this country at the
OL,8,Fmoment are unbearable.
OL,10,F"I think the mismanagement of pretty
OL,11,Fmuch everything in this country at the
OL,12,Fmoment by our government is hurting
OL,13,Feveryone in the business so much -
OL,14,Fspecially hospitality, especially the
OL,15,Fshops, especially the small businesses.
OL,17,F"The food inflation we've had is
OL,18,Fcrazy. The taxes, the PAYE that we've
OL,19,Fhad to put on the wages last year has
OL,20,Fabsolutely killed us and many others.
