OL,3,CPopular shop announces closure due to
OL,4,C'unbearable trading conditions'
OL,6,F"We've lost our little farm shop
OL,7,Fthat's meant a lot to us and we've
OL,8,Fworked very hard on it over the years.
OL,9,FBut if the figures don't add up, they
OL,10,Fdon't add up.
OL,12,F"At the moment, we lose money every
OL,13,Fday by opening. It's hurt us very
OL,14,Fmuch, especially on our hearts...It's
OL,15,Fa sad day."
OL,17,FHe praised the staff at the shop, some
OL,18,Fof whom have worked there for more
OL,19,Fthan 15 years. He also encouraged
OL,20,Fpeople to support the farm and other
OL,21,Flocal businesses in their areas.
