OL,6,F"We've built this farm shop by our
OL,7,Fbare hands and now we're having to
OL,8,Fclose it," he said.
OL,10,F"The main thing I'm saying to you guys
OL,11,Fis you need to support us at the Cefn
OL,12,FMably farm...You need to look around
OL,13,Fand look after all your local
OL,14,Fbusinesses."
