OL,6,FLast month, the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fannounced #116 million to help
OL,8,Fbusinesses manage those rate changes
OL,9,Ffollowing the reevaluation of property
OL,10,Fvalues coming into effect in April
OL,11,F2026. It added that the reevaluation
OL,12,Fof business rates could see some small
OL,13,Fbusinesses find their bills fall and
OL,14,Fsome others will have the increase
OL,15,Fphased in over the next two years.
