OL,3,CPopular shop announces closure due to
OL,4,C'unbearable trading conditions'
OL,6,FThe Finance Secretary Mark Drakeford
OL,7,Fsaid: "We know businesses have faced
OL,8,Fsignificant economic challenges in
OL,9,Frecent years. This support package
OL,10,Fwill help them manage the transition
OL,11,Fto updated rates bills while we
OL,12,Fdeliver on our commitment to a fairer
OL,13,Frates system.
OL,15,F"By introducing more frequent
OL,16,Frevaluations and a lower rate for
OL,17,Fsmall shops, we're making sure the
OL,18,Fbusiness rates system reflects today's
OL,19,Feconomy and supports the businesses
OL,20,Fthat are the backbone of our high
OL,21,Fstreets and communities."
