OL,6,FThe rise in employer's National
OL,7,FInsurance Contributions announced in
OL,8,F2024 was described by the Chancellor
OL,9,Fas the "hardest decision" she made in
OL,10,Fthat budget. The UK Government said
OL,11,Fthe rise was needed to help fund
OL,12,Fpublic services.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday (14 January), the
OL,15,FChancellor confirmed that the
OL,16,Fgovernment would be offering "more
OL,17,Ftemporary support" to pubs in England
OL,18,Fto help them cover the cost of rising
OL,19,Fbusiness rates, after concern from
OL,20,Fthose in the hospitality industry.
